5000|$|Marquardt {{appeared}} on news programs including NBC’s Today, CNN, ABC, FOX, CBS, and PBS, BBC World News and {{national and local}} NPR stations. She published opinion pieces in the New York Times, Washington Post, Los Angeles Times, Slate, Huffington Post, and The Atlantic online. Her peer-reviewed single authored and co-authored chapters appeared in Social Science Research, John Marshall Law Review, and Sociology of Religion, and in volumes from New York University Press and Paradigm Press. She was a <b>scholar</b> <b>at</b> <b>the</b> Institute for <b>American</b> Values from 2000-2013. In spring 2013, she was a lecturer in American Studies at Lake Forest College.|$|R
